			<p><small><a href="/Vatican_Saying_33" title="Vatican Saying 33">&lt;&lt;Prev</a> | <a href="/Vatican_Sayings" title="Vatican Sayings">Vatican Sayings</a> | <a href="/Vatican_Saying_35" title="Vatican Saying 35">Next&gt;&gt;</a></small>
</p>
<div id='interlinear'><span><p class='script150'><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:Οὐχ' title='Ouch: Not'><font color='#000000'>Οὐχ</font></a>&nbsp;</p><br><p><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:Οὐχ' title='1) Not'><font color='#000000'>→</font></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></span><span><p class='script150'><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:οὕτως' title='houtos: thus'><font color='#000000'>οὕτως</font></a>&nbsp;</p><br><p><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:οὕτως' title='2) thus'><font color='#000000'>→</font></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></span><span><p class='script150'><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:χρείαν' title='chreian: need'><font color='#000000'>χρείαν</font></a>&nbsp;</p><br><p><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:χρείαν' title='3) need'><font color='#000000'>→</font></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></span><span><p class='script150'><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:ἔχομεν' title='echomen: we have'><font color='#000000'>ἔχομεν</font></a>&nbsp;</p><br><p><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:ἔχομεν' title='4) we have'><font color='#000000'>We have [no need]</font></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></span><span><p class='script150'><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:τῆς' title='tes: of the'><font color='#000000'>τῆς</font></a>&nbsp;</p><br><p><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:τῆς' title='5) of the'><font color='#000000'> of the</font></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></span><span><p class='script150'><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:χρείας' title='chreias: utility'><font color='#000000'>χρείας</font></a>&nbsp;</p><br><p><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:χρείας' title='6) utility'><font color='#000000'>utility [per se]</font></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></span><span><p class='script150'><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:τῆς' title='tes: of the'><font color='#000000'>τῆς</font></a>&nbsp;</p><br><p><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:τῆς' title='7) of the'><font color='#000000'>→</font></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></span><span><p class='script150'><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:παρὰ' title='para: by'><font color='#000000'>παρὰ</font></a>&nbsp;</p><br><p><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:παρὰ' title='8) by; at; on; despite'><font color='#000000'>(that we derive) from</font></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></span><span><p class='script150'><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:τῶν' title='ton: the'><font color='#000000'>τῶν</font></a>&nbsp;</p><br><p><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:τῶν' title='9) the; of the; that of; what is; of what is; from the; of those things; of those people'><font color='#000000'>→</font></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></span><span><p class='script150'><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:φίλων' title='philon: friends'><font color='#000000'>φίλων</font></a>&nbsp;</p><br><p><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:φίλων' title='10) friends'><font color='#000000'> friends</font></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></span><span><p class='script150'><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:ὡς' title='os: as'><font color='#000000'>ὡς</font></a>&nbsp;</p><br><p><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:ὡς' title='11) as; as if; that; since'><font color='#000000'>(we rather need)</font></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></span><span><p class='script150'><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:τῆς' title='tes: of the'><font color='#000000'>τῆς</font></a>&nbsp;</p><br><p><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:τῆς' title='12) of the'><font color='#000000'>→</font></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></span><span><p class='script150'><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:πίστεως' title='pisteos:faith'><font color='#000000'>πίστεως</font></a>&nbsp;</p><br><p><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:πίστεως' title='13) faith; confidence'><font color='#000000'>confidence</font></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></span><span><p class='script150'><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:τῆς' title='tes: of the'><font color='#000000'>τῆς</font></a>&nbsp;</p><br><p><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:τῆς' title='14) of the'><font color='#000000'>→</font></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></span><span><p class='script150'><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:περὶ' title='peri: about'><font color='#000000'>περὶ</font></a>&nbsp;</p><br><p><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:περὶ' title='15) about; regarding; surrounding'><font color='#000000'>regarding</font></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></span><span><p class='script150'><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:τῆς' title='tes: of the'><font color='#000000'>τῆς</font></a>&nbsp;</p><br><p><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:τῆς' title='16) of the'><font color='#000000'>→</font></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></span><span><p class='script150'><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:χρείας' title='chreias: utility'><font color='#000000'>χρείας.</font></a>&nbsp;</p><br><p><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:χρείας' title='17) utility'><font color='#000000'>[this] utility (should we ever need it)</font></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></span><span><p><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=template:Vatican Saying 34 Text' title='Vatican Saying 34 Text'><img src='http://www.epicurus.info/scroll.gif'></a></p></span></div>
<a name="Translation"></a><h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/iurl/index.php?title=Vatican_Saying_34&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: Translation">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline"> Translation </span></h2>
<p><big><a href="/iurl/index.php?title=Template:Vatican_Saying_34&amp;action=edit" class="new" title="Template:Vatican Saying 34">Template:Vatican Saying 34</a></big>
</p>
<a name="Analysis"></a><h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/iurl/index.php?title=Vatican_Saying_34&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2" title="Edit section: Analysis">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline"> Analysis </span></h2>
<p>Refining his teaching on the benefits of <a href="/Friendship" title="Friendship">friendship</a>, Epicurus clarifies that we do not need the "utility", the utilitarian benefits that we derive from our friendships on an ongoing basis; what we do need instead is the underlying feeling of confidence and security, as we rest assured that, should we call upon our friends in an hour of need, they will be there to help us out. This is in line with the broader Epicuran belief that friends are the pillars of our personal <a href="/Security" title="Security">security</a>.
</p><div class="printfooter">
Retrieved from "<a href="http://wiki.epicurism.info/Vatican_Saying_34">http://wiki.epicurism.info/Vatican_Saying_34</a>"</div>
